N_ves = len(points)

cells = []

for k in range(N_ves):
    
    (x, y) = (list(), list())
    pnt_id = vor.point_region[k]
    for idx in vor.regions[pnt_id]:
        x.append(vor.vertices[idx][0])
        y.append(vor.vertices[idx][1])
            
    vertices = np.array( [x, y] ).transpose()
    cells.append( shp.Polygon(vertices) )

d = tls.load_constants_from_file('/home/andrey/WORK/PyScripts/VesiclesInitialization/constants_for_fun_with_obstacles.txt')

d['kl'] = 3.0

vesicles_out = []

for cell in cells_trials:
    
    resize_value = (314.0/abs(cell.area()))**(1/2)
    sh_x = cell.make_nodes(113).resize(resize_value).vertices[0:-1,0]
    sh_y = cell.make_nodes(113).resize(resize_value).vertices[0:-1,1]

    v_x = sh_x*0.0
    v_y = sh_x*0.0

    V = shp.Variable(sh_x, sh_y, v_x, v_y)
    
    shots = []
    out = AME.simulate(X = V, walls = cell, output = None,
                       t_end = 10, frames = 10,
                       ADAPTIVE = True,
                       function = fnc.fun_with_obstacles, constants = d)
    
    vesicles_out.append(out[-1])
